1
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:19,680
Xin'er.

2
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,120
Is that you?

3
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,040
Mother. Xin'er.

4
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,000
We might need to stay away

5
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,720
for a while.

6
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,460
Well...

7
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,610
Why do we have to move again?

8
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,280
Xin'er,

9
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,400
could you go beg that noble lady?

10
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:33,400
We used to move every three years.

11
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,160
It hasn't even been a year yet.

12
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,480
Can we delay it a bit?

13
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,140
Mother,

14
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,800
we might have to make a living on our own from now on.

15
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,260
Well...

16
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,960
Did you offend that noble lady?

17
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,600
She has been so good to us.

18
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,800
She gave us such a nice house,

19
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,720
and sent us money every month.

20
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,600
You mustn't let her down.

21
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,579
Mother,

22
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,840
just listen to me.

23
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,040
Pack up quickly,

24
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,920
or we'll lose our lives.

25
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,000
Oh.

26
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:00,800
Also,

27
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,080
the small box I asked you to keep last time,

28
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,010
find it quickly.

29
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,360
Huiwen!

30
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,280
Huiwen!

31
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:07,800
Huiwen!

32
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,640
Sister,

33
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,240
you're back.

34
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,060
Huiwen,

35
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,290
pack up quickly.

36
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,920
We must leave at once.

37
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,760
Hurry up.

38
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:09,560
The sacrificial ceremony begins.

39
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,050
Consort Yu didn't know at this time

40
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,720
that after the ceremony,

41
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,540
she would become a prisoner forever.

42
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,500
I followed Aunt Huixin all the way

43
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,600
and finally retrieved the key evidence

44
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,600
of Consort Yu's murder of Queen Yun.

45
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,340
I rushed back to the palace in time

46
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,920
and presented it to King Yunqiu in person.

47
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,400
King Yunqiu was furious.

48
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,560
On the spot,

49
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,330
he banished Consort Yu to the Cold Palace.

50
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,560
I owe Yunchuan,

51
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,680
so this should make up for it.

52
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,200
Next,

53
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,210
I should do what I have to do.

54
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,580
Ling Xuele.

55
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,640
Ling Xuele.

56
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,600
What are you thinking about?

57
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,800
You look distracted.

58
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,560
Nothing.

59
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,560
Are you thinking about

60
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,600
leaving?

61
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:29,770
I was too suspicious of you before.

62
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,800
Today I realized you truly want to help His Highness.

63
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,640
From my observation these days,

64
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:37,530
His Highness also hopes you will stay.

65
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,920
I will only bring him more trouble.

66
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,960
Why would he want me to stay?

67
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,220
That's because

68
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,680
the spectator sees more than the player.

69
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,810
But I see it clearly.

70
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,840
His Highness treats you

71
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,300
differently from others.

72
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,100
I didn't expect

73
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,170
you to be so brave

74
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,800
to distract the assassins and save Aunt Huixin,

75
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,880
helping us get the evidence to overthrow Consort Yu.

76
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,010
If you really leave,

77
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,050
who would His Highness and I

78
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,280
repay?

79
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,900
Let's not talk about this now.

80
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,850
Is His Highness in his room?

81
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,770
He's been locked inside for hours.

82
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,400
Speaking of today,

83
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,130
it should have been a happy day.

84
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,040
The truth about Queen Yun's death is clear,

85
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,520
and the culprit has been executed.

86
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,050
But on His Highness's face,

87
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,200
I don't see a hint of joy.

88
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,040
Even so,

89
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,880
how can what is lost

90
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,480
ever be brought back?

91
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,800
He just needs some time alone right now.

92
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:45,680
Today is the anniversary of Queen Yun's death.

93
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,940
Isn't that His Highness's birthday?

94
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,800
Yes.

95
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,600
How could I have forgotten that?

96
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,320
Come here.

97
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,280
You always have the best ideas.

98
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:03,760
Go on.

99
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,280
Okay.

100
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,800
Stop right there.

101
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,960
How dare you serve me

102
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,640
this disgusting food?

103
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,400
Consort Yu,

104
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,480
this is all we have here.

105
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,960
Whether you want to or not,

106
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:34,960
you have to eat it.

107
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,360
Is that how you speak to me?

108
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,520
Believe it or not,

109
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,159
when I get out of here,

110
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,460
I'll kill every single one of you.

111
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,720
Do you still think

112
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,720
you're a high-and-mighty consort?

113
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,580
Let me tell you,

114
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,970
no one who comes here

115
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,920
ever walks out in one piece.

116
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,280
You insolent servant!

117
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,050
How dare you talk back to me?

118
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,840
We remember very well

119
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,850
how you usually treated us.

120
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,680
I advise you

121
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,520
to stop making a fuss.

122
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,740
Otherwise,

123
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,040
your days ahead

124
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,850
will be even harder.

125
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,440
You!

126
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,300
You insolent servant!

127
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,240
Get out of here!

128
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,400
Get out!

129
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,040
Get out!

130
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,490
I still have one unfulfilled wish in my heart.

131
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,400
I wonder if you'll be happy for me

132
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,080
when you hear it, Mother.

133
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,720
I originally thought there was no one

134
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,850
left in this world for me to care about.

135
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,440
The passion of love

136
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,120
is ultimately fleeting.

137
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,220
If I can't grow old with the one I love,

138
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:02,260
why involve those innocent women

139
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,320
in this senseless

140
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,300
struggle for royal power?

141
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,280
After all I've been through,

142
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,200
I've met someone.

143
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,760
Someone I

144
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,740
am willing to give up everything to protect.

145
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,090
I just don't know her feelings.

146
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,490
If our feelings are mutual,

147
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,260
I am willing to give up everything

148
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,400
to protect her.

149
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,080
And marry her.

150
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,240
No matter what,

151
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,880
you must never forget

152
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:43,840
that Yunchuan is the son of the man who destroyed our country.

153
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,440
Yunchuan.

154
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,000
I want nothing more than to confess my feelings

155
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,720
to you.

156
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,440
But I must avenge my country,

157
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,800
and I don't want to let you down

158
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:57,000
or use you.

159
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,200
Or use you.

160
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,600
So I can only choose to leave.

161
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,050
Ling Xue'le.

162
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,320
What are you doing here?

163
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,650
Why aren't you going in?

164
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,100
Your Highness,

165
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:19,280
What wine would you like for dinner?

166
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,520
The usual.

167
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,460
Same as always.

168
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,560
Then I will go prepare it.

169
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,240
Your Highness,

170
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,500
Lady Pingle seems to have drunk too much.

171
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:18,560
Xue'le.

172
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,400
Xue'le.

173
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,000
Tingfeng.

174
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,560
Tingfeng.

175
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,120
Coming, coming, coming.

176
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,240
Lady Xue'le usually

177
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,440
does this.

178
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,800
I'm just imitating her.

179
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,260
Hurry and call the doctor.

180
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,120
What?

181
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:34,800
Hurry.

182
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:36,530
Okay.

183
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:39,500
Your Highness,

184
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,240
I'll leave

185
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:41,880
the soup here for you.

186
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,400
Xue'le.

187
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,040
Xue'le.

188
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,600
How is she?

189
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:57,720
May I ask

190
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,320
if Lady Xue'le ate

191
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:01,640
anything unusual?

192
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,460
We've been eating the same food these past few days.

193
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,060
There's nothing unusual.

194
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:08,920
Besides,

195
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,160
she was perfectly fine during the day.

196
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:11,760
Could it be

197
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:14,140
that she secretly ate something?

198
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,640
Tonight,

199
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,450
she drank a little wine.

200
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,450
Could it be related to this?

201
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:20,980
Your Highness,

202
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,820
Lady Xue'le is exhibiting

203
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,090
symptoms of poisoning.

204
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,280
Poisoned?

205
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,000
In my opinion,

206
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,200
this poison

207
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,760
has been in her body

208
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,050
for quite some time.

209
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,080
It is exactly because of the wine

210
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:38,120
that the spread of the poison accelerated.

211
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,360
What kind of poison is it?

212
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,980
And when was she poisoned?

213
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,000
I'm afraid it's been more than a few months.

214
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:47,880
As for the poison,

215
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:50,960
please forgive my incompetence, Your Highness.

216
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,600
I cannot identify it yet.

217
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,560
However,

218
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,840
Your Highness does not need to be overly anxious.

219
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:59,480
I can perform acupuncture on Lady Xue'le first

220
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,060
to seal her meridians.

221
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,720
As long as the poison doesn't invade her internal organs,

222
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:05,360
her life will be safe for now.

223
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,160
Okay.

224
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:07,520
Then I'll have to trouble you

225
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:09,720
to perform acupuncture on her quickly.

226
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,580
Please.

227
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,020
Your Highness.

228
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,560
Lady Xue'le

229
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,520
has only been in the palace for a few months.

230
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,120
Could it be

231
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:27,160
that she was poisoned before entering the palace?

232
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,320
But

233
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:33,000
why would she hide it from us?
